## Technology Stack

| Concern | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict mode) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS |
| Testing | Jest + React Testing Library |
| E2E Testing | Playwright |
| HTTP Client | fetch (native) or axios |
| Forms | React Hook Form (if needed) |

---

## Architecture Overview

```
app/                    # Next.js App Router — pages, layouts, routes
components/             # Reusable UI components (Server and Client)
  ui/                   # Atomic/primitive components (Button, Input, Card...)
  shared/               # Composite components used across features
  [feature]/            # Feature-specific components
hooks/                  # Custom React hooks (client-side)
lib/                    # Utilities, API clients, helpers
  api/                  # API service functions
  utils/                # Pure utility functions
types/                  # Shared TypeScript types and interfaces
```

---

